    <title><![CDATA[Tidio Integration]]></title>
    <link>https://pikapikapikaori.github.io/pikapikapi-blog/#/pages/hexo/themes/hexo-theme-cupertino/docs/integrations/tidio</link>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">https://pikapikapikaori.github.io/pikapikapi-blog/#/pages/hexo/themes/hexo-theme-cupertino/docs/integrations/tidio</guid>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="tidio-integration">Tidio Integration</h1><p>We support installing Tidio to your blog.</p><ol type="1"><li><p>Go to <a href="https://www.tidio.com/panel/settings/live-chat/integration">Tidio Settings/Channels/Live Chat/Integration</a>.</p></li><li><p>Click “click here”.</p></li><li><p>Select “JavaScript”.</p></li><li><p>Copy the URL in the code it provided. <img src="./img/tidio-integration-url.png" alt="Screenshot of the settings page and the integration url" /></p></li><li><p>Add <code>tidio</code> property to your blog configuration <code>_config.yml</code>:</p><div class="sourceCode" id="cb1"><pre class="sourceCode yml"><code class="sourceCode yaml"><span id="cb1-1"><a href="#cb1-1" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="co">...</span></span><span id="cb1-2"><a href="#cb1-2" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="co">tidio: &lt;the-url-you-copied-in-the-previous-step&gt;</span></span><span id="cb1-3"><a href="#cb1-3" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="co">...</span></span></code></pre></div></li><li><p>Done!</p></li></ol>]]></content>
    <pubDate>Sat, 2 Nov 2024 22:21:32 +0800</pubDate>
  </entry>
   
