    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="latex">LaTeX</h1><p>You don’t need to change any theme config exactly, and you can choose the renderer you like from the following:</p><ul><li><a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-math">hexo-math</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-filter-mathjax">Hexo Filter MathJax</a></li></ul><p>Just follow their documentation to install them, no further configuration required.</p><blockquote><p>Plot <span class="math inline">(<em>x</em><sup>2</sup> + <em>y</em><sup>2</sup> − 1)<sup>3</sup> − <em>x</em><sup>2</sup><em>y</em><sup>3</sup> = 0</span>. 💖 from <span class="citation" data-cites="aeilot">[@aeilot's PR]</span>(https://github.com/MrWillCom/hexo-theme-cupertino/pull/9)</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    <pubDate>Sat, 2 Nov 2024 22:21:32 +0800</pubDate>
